<br>
This forum is to discuss things not EQ related.  Yes, there are worlds outside of Norrath and Luclin!<br>
<br>
If you wish, you can come in here and tell us abut your real lives and your other interests.  Or just share a joke or two.  (Please keep them clean, or run the risk of being deleted... and spanked!)<br>
<br>
<br>
I guess I'll start out by telling you folks a little about myself.<br>
<br>
My name is Ric.  I live near Albany, NY.  That's about 2 and a half - 3 hours North of NYC.  I am a TV News Photographer at the local ABC affiliate and have been there for almost 15 years.  For the last 2 years I have been working in the investigative unit.  Mostly, we concentrate on the consumer end of things, like contractors ripping folks off and the like.<br>
<br>
Over the past 15 years I thought I saw every kind of story possible.  Until that fateful day a year ago September.  Now, I don't think anything can surprise me...  <br>
<br>
Anyway, my other computer related interests are (in case you couldn't guess) working on websites and playing with PhotoShop.<br>
<br>
I also am a BIG Hometheater buff.  I have almost 400 DVDs and my RL Epic quest is to convince my wife to let me get one of those beautiful new Widescreen  Rear Projection TVs!  That's probably another year or two away as I continue to chip away at her defenses!<br>
<br>
If any of the rest of you are interested in Home Theater, there is a excellent forum dedicated to it at...  www.hometheaterforum.com<br>
<br>
I also like playing other games.  And have been a big fan of FPS (First Person Shooters) and Space Combat sims.  Some of my favorites have been Half-Life, Unreal, and Freespace 1 and 2.<br>
<br>
Recently I have been playing Earth and Beyond.  It's kind of an Everquest in space.  I'll tell you more about that one later...<br>
<br>
Right now I have to go off to war!  <br>
<br>
Kam/Ric <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000028><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub135.ezboard.com/usingsang.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SingSang</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 668<br> <font color=#A8A8A8>(10/13/02 12:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub135.ezboard.com/fexodusfellowshipforumfrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.exodusfellowship.com/Sing-B.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_mad.gif" align=absmiddle>  GIVE ME A BREAK!</span><hr size=1> OK Ric - give me a break here. &quot;Until that fateful day...&quot; and no followup? COME ON!<br>
